com.inmobi.androidsdk
Class IMAdRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.inmobi.androidsdk.IMAdRequest

public class IMAdRequest
extends Object

IMAdRequest is used to provide extra information when getting ads. It is primarily used for better targeting and to set the test mode.
